titles: An act appointing judges for the Admiralty.
author: England and Wales. Parliament.
publisher: Printed by John Field, Printer to the Parliament. And are to be sold at the seven Stars in Fleetstreet, over against Dunstans Church,
notes: Appointing John Godolphin and Charles George Cock to be judges of the admiralty until 10 December 1659.
Order to print dated: Tuesday, July 19. 1659. Signed: Tho. St Nicholas clerk of the Parliament.
Reproduction of the original in the British Library.
